| Feature               | Example                       | Description                |
| --------------------- | ----------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| **Template literals** | `` `Hello ${name}` ``         | String interpolation       |
| **Destructuring**     | `const {x,y} = obj`           | Extract values easily      |
